body_html: I get that, but they already went out of their way by changing tf.logging.set_verbosity(tf.logging.ERROR). I'm fine with warnings by default, but there ought to be documented way to get rid of unwanted messages. Just like compiler warnings. Maybe something like tf.logging.set_perf_reports(0).
